programme.desc: «Rock Star's Miami Mansion & Billionaire's Custom Train»Rock out in the Miami Mansion where Lenny Kravitz left some posh personal touches. Enter "The Vault," an uber-exclusive car club for a group of billionaire neighbors. Be dazzled by the one-of-a-kind pieces of jewelry hiding secret treasures where you'd least expect. Run up your bar tab with a nearly $40,000 bottle of cognac. Tour the one-of-a-kind townhouse just steps away from Madonna's Upper East Side mansion. Check out the $20 million sports memorabilia collection that includes a massive sneaker stockpile. And go under the hood of the vintage hot rods that are being transformed into million-dollar modern marvels.
